            "failure_message": "Requires dread as the primary signal with threat-axis grounding and negative valence; keeps arousal in the 'heavy bracing' band; keeps engagement from collapsing and explicitly excludes dissociation; stays below panic/terror extremes, excludes freeze, and fires only on dread crossing/spike or a sharp threat-axis jump."
